IMAPAccount posteo
Host posteo.de
User erg@posteo.net
PassCmd "~/.local/bin/pass-filter Mail/Posteo"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore posteo-remote
Account posteo

MaildirStore posteo-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/posteo/
Inbox ~/.mail/posteo/Inbox
Trash ~/.mail/posteo/Trash
TrashNewOnly yes
TrashRemoteNew yes

Channel posteo
Master :posteo-remote:
Slave :posteo-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
Expunge Both
